<a href="/articlesguides/holidays/christmas/christmascookiesminiblackandwhites/recipes/food/views/MINI-BLACK-AND-WHITE-COOKIES-233293"><h3>Mini Black-and-White Cookies</h3></a>

<br /><br />
<p><span class="dropCapFirst">A</span>
New York classic is downsized into the perfect holiday treat. For a clean division  between the chocolate and vanilla icing, use a creased piece of foil or wax paper as a straightedge. </p> 

